			<div class="content" id="post-content-4132252">
									

<p>Okay, so&#8230; this was a long time coming.</p>
<p>This page is to provide information on some of our preeminent reviewers, in an attempt to help authors figure out who can best help them with their particular drafts at hand. We have a lot of skilled reviewers who specialize in all sorts of works!</p>
<p>We're mostly staff, but there's still lots of room on the Squad for any talented and active critique-givers in the community who are looking to make a name for themselves as a Butterfly. Being added to the Roster used to be on an invitation-only basis and still is to some extent; however, we like to encourage reviewers to take the initiative to reach out to us!</p>
<p><span style="color: blue">If you would like to join the team and be added to this list, please first send a wikidot or chat message to me (<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1404533); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1404533&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604554123" alt="Zyn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1404533)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1404533); return false;">Zyn</a></span>) stating your interest and why you believe you would be an asset to both the team and the site at large.</span></p>
<p>Noting here the coding for members who have requested to be removed from the active PM listing, due to other commitments and obligations. We thank you for your service!</p>
